      </p>
      <ul class="mb-4">
        <li>Western Naval Command - Mumbai</li>
        <li>Eastern Naval Command - Visakhapatnam</li>
        <li>Southern Naval Command - Kochi</li>
        <li class="text-teal-400">Tri-services Command - Port Blair</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This underscores our comprehensive reach and steadfast commitment to bolstering the Indian Navy across diverse geographical locations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/2 mt-8 md:mt-0 flex justify-center">
      <img src="/india-map.png" alt="Indian Navy Commands" class="w-full" />
    </div>
